originalSql:
SELECT 
    p.Id AS PostId,
    p.Title,
    p.CreationDate AS PostCreationDate,
    u.DisplayName AS OwnerDisplayName,
    u.Reputation AS OwnerReputation,
    COALESCE(vote_counts.UpVotes, 0) AS UpVoteCount,
    COALESCE(vote_counts.DownVotes, 0) AS DownVoteCount,
    COALESCE(c_counts.CommentCount, 0) AS CommentCount,
    COALESCE(badge_counts.BadgeCount, 0) AS UserBadgeCount
FROM 
    Posts p
JOIN 
    Users u ON p.OwnerUserId = u.Id
LEFT JOIN 
    (SELECT 
        PostId,
        SUM(CASE WHEN VoteTypeId = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS UpVotes,
        SUM(CASE WHEN VoteTypeId = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DownVotes
     FROM 
        Votes
     GROUP BY 
        PostId) vote_counts ON p.Id = vote_counts.PostId
LEFT JOIN 
    (SELECT 
        PostId,
        COUNT(Id) AS CommentCount
     FROM 
        Comments
     GROUP BY 
        PostId) c_counts ON p.Id = c_counts.PostId
LEFT JOIN 
    (SELECT 
        UserId,
        COUNT(Id) AS BadgeCount
     FROM 
        Badges
     GROUP BY 
        UserId) badge_counts ON u.Id = badge_counts.UserId
WHERE 
    p.PostTypeId = 1 
ORDER BY 
    p.CreationDate DESC
LIMIT 100

GROUP BY "PostId") AS "t5" ON "Posts"."Id" = "t5"."POSTID"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "Users"."Id" = "s1"."USERID"
WHERE CAST("Posts"."PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1
ORDER BY "Posts"."CreationDate" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 100

SELECT COALESCE("UserId", "UserId") AS "USERID"
FROM "Badges"

SELECT COALESCE("Posts"."Id", "Posts"."Id") AS "POSTID", "Posts"."Title" AS "TITLE", "Posts"."CreationDate" AS "POSTCREATIONDATE", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "OWNERDISPLAYNAME", "Users"."Reputation" AS "OWNERREPUTATION", CASE WHEN "t2"."UPVOTES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t2"."UPVOTES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "UPVOTECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t2"."DOWNVOTES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t2"."DOWNVOTES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "DOWNVOTECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."COMMENTCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."COMMENTCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "COMMENTCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t5"."BADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t5"."BADGECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "USERBADGECOUNT"
FROM "Posts"
INNER JOIN "Users" ON "Posts"."OwnerUserId" = "Users"."Id"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "PostId" AS "POSTID", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("VoteTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "UPVOTES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("VoteTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "DOWNVOTES"
FROM "Votes"
GROUP BY "PostId") AS "t2" ON "Posts"."Id" = "t2"."POSTID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "PostId" AS "POSTID", COUNT(*) AS "COMMENTCOUNT"
FROM "Comments"
GROUP BY "PostId") AS "t4" ON "Posts"."Id" = "t4"."POSTID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "USERID", COUNT(*) AS "BADGECOUNT"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "USERID") AS "t5" ON "Users"."Id" = "t5"."USERID"
WHERE CAST("Posts"."PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1
ORDER BY "Posts"."CreationDate" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 100
